title: Frank Lloyd Wright House Beautiful Guest Book
description:
This guest book makes a welcoming addition to your coffee table or entryway.
The foil stamped cover is inspired by Wright's designs evoking ironwork and Middle Eastern tapestries originally published in his book, The House Beautiful.  Includes 64 lined sheets of paper with gilded sprayed edge and ribbon page marker.  Perfect for parties and celebratory events such as weddings and showers.

10 x 7 3/4 in.
